OL,3,CMan pleads guilty over 'death threat'
OL,4,Cgun video posted after Southport
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FA Birmingham man has admitted making
OL,8,Fthreats of death or serious harm
OL,9,Ftowards members of the English Defence
OL,10,FLeague in a video which went viral
OL,11,Fduring last summer's riots.
OL,13,FHabeeb Khan was arrested in early
OL,14,FAugust after a video featuring him
OL,15,Fholding an imitation AK-47 was posted
OL,16,Fon social media.
