OL,3,CMan pleads guilty over 'death threat'
OL,4,Cgun video posted after Southport
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThe 49-year-old, dressed all in black,
OL,8,Fincluding gloves, sunglasses and a
OL,9,Fface covering, was seen on the video
OL,10,Fswearing and making threats towards
OL,11,Fthe EDL and the defunct group's former
OL,12,Fleader Tommy Robinson.
OL,14,FKhan, of Hickman Road, Sparkbrook,
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty on Monday, November 18,
OL,16,Fat Birmingham Crown Court to a charge
OL,17,Fof sending a communication threatening
OL,18,Fdeath or serious harm.
