OL,7,FKhan pleaded not guilty to a second
OL,8,Fcharge of possessing an imitation
OL,9,Ffirearm, a plea which the Crown
OL,10,Faccepted. The defendant was remanded
OL,11,Fin custody for sentencing next month.
OL,13,FDefence barrister Sunit Sandhu said
OL,14,FKhan was suffering from mental health
OL,15,Fdifficulties for which he was on
OL,16,Fmedication.
