OL,7,FAdjourning the case, Judge Melbourne
OL,8,FInman KC told Khan: "You will be
OL,9,Fsentenced on the 19th of December. I
OL,10,Fwill direct that there is a pre-
OL,11,Fsentence report.
OL,13,F"That's not an indication of (the type
OL,14,Fof) sentence, but it's important that
OL,15,FI know as much about you and your
OL,16,Fbackground as possible."
